<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id1434d1ea-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id1434d1eb-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2022—Subsec. (a)(4). <ref href="/us/pl/117/286">Pub. L. 117–286</ref> substituted “<ref href="/us/usc/t5/s1013">Section 1013 of title 5</ref>” for “Section 14 of the Federal Advisory Committee Act”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
